# CNG / Prebuild — force EAS to regenerate iOS from app.json on every
# build instead of reusing a stale committed folder. Recommended by
# expo-doctor when app.json has plugins but the ios/ folder is absent
# from the repo (our current state).
# https://docs.expo.dev/workflow/prebuild/#usage-with-eas-build
/ios
